question: Which Indian cyclist won gold in the men's junior Keirin event at the 2019 Asian Track Cycling Championships
explanation: Indian cyclist Ronaldo Singh has won gold in the men\'s junior Keirin event at the 2019 Asian Track Cycling Championships at Incheon in South Korea. Apart from Ronaldo, James Singh clinched a bronze medal in the same event. India also secured 2 bronze medals in men’s and women’s Jr. sprint team.
